flowchart TB
    N1["1. neo-bridge-watcher-tron: Trust boundary shows what must be proven rather than believed."]
    N2["2. Trusted base: confirmation policy, message format, nonce rules, asset mapping"]
    N3["3. Untrusted input: TRON RPC/log stream | bridge contract events | checkpoint cursor"]
    N4["4. Validation boundary: event, confirmations, message hash, nonce, and asset state all pass"]
    N5["5. Replay and ordering: nonce, source height, and message hash provide ordering and replay protection"]
    N6["6. Authority: asset actions require bridge rules, message evidence, and governance policy"]
    N7["7. External systems: L1/L2 RPC, heterogeneous chains, watchers, gateway, asset contracts"]
    N8["8. Observed evidence: source event, confirmations, message hash, cursor, submit hash, and final state"]
    N1 --> N2
    N1 --> N3
    N1 --> N4
    N1 --> N5
    N1 --> N6
    N1 --> N7
    N1 --> N8
    N2 -. constrains .-> N4
    N4 -. produces .-> N5
    N5 -. consumed by .-> N6
